oai_dc:dc.dc:title: EXPERIMENTAL SHOREFACE NOURISHMENT, TERSCHELLING (NL)
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Mulder, J.P.M.
van de Kreeke, J.
van Vessem, P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: nourishment
experimental nourishment
Terschelling
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An experimental shoreface nourishment was implemented at Terschelling, the Netherlands in 1993. The effectiveness of this nourishment will be evaluated in the framework of an EU sponsored project NOURTEC. The design of the Terschelling nourishment including the objectives and alternatives, are described in detail. Preliminary monitoring results lead to a cautious optimism with regard to the performance of the nourishment.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 24 (1994): Proceedings of 24th Conference on Coastal Engineering, Kobe, Japan, 1994.
